t Submission.'\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://bitcointodays.com/write-for-us/\",\n      \"domain\": \"bitcointodays.com\",\n      \"type\": \"guest_post\",\n      \"title\": \"Submit a Guest Post Cryptocurrency - Write For Us - Bitcoin Todays\",\n      \"relevance_notes\": \"A premium Bitcoin-focused news site accepting cryptocurrency-related guest contributions. Matches Coinography's niche perfectly.\",\n      \"submission_url\": \"https://bitcointodays.com/contact-us/\",\n      \"guidelines_snippet\": \"Only original, unique, relevant, well-written content will be considered. Posts should be 500-1000 words. Contact: guestpost.frank@gmail.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://absolutecryptos.com/submit-a-guest-post/\",\n      \"domain\": \"absolutecryptos.com\",\n      \"type\": \"guest_post\",\n      \"title\": \"Submit a Guest Post | Absolute Cryptos\",\n      \"relevance_notes\": \"Dedicated crypto-news and directory blog accepting descriptive guidelines and news-worthy guest post articles.\",\n      \"submission_url\": \"https://absolutecryptos.com/submit-a-guest-post/\",\n      \"guidelines_snippet\": \"Article must be above 400+ words. No English and grammatical mistakes. Contact: vehementmedia12@gmail.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://thebeforeitsnews.com/write-for-us-news-and-media/\",\n      \"domain\": \"thebeforeitsnews.com\",\n      \"type\": \"guest_post\",\n      \"title\": \"Write for Us News: Guide to Contributing to Google News, Entertainment, Tech, and More\",\n      \"relevance_notes\": \"An alternative media platform accepting crypto, tech, and Google News syndication. Excellent opportunity to secure a high-exposure backlink.\",\n      \"submission_url\": \"https://thebeforeitsnews.com/contact/\",\n      \"guidelines_snippet\": \"Each site will have specific submission guidelines. Start today and share your knowledge with the world! Contact: thebeforeitsnews@gmail.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.scrolltrendy.com/cryptocurrency-write-for-us/\",\n      \"domain\": \"scrolltrendy.com\",\n      \"type\": \"guest_post\",\n      \"title\": \"Write For Us + Crypto | Submit Guest Posts NFT, Bitcoin, DeFi\",\n      \"relevance_notes\": \"Trend-focused cryptocurrency blog accepting articles about NFT, Bitcoin, DeFi, and blockchain applications.\",\n      \"submission_url\": \"https://www.scrolltrendy.com/cryptocurrency-write-for-us/\",\n      \"guidelines_snippet\": \"We require plagiarism free unique content. Article words should be above 600. Email: scrolltrendy@gmail.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.cryptowebwire.com/guest-posting\",\n      \"domain\": \"cryptowebwire.com\",\n      \"type\": \"guest_post\",\n      \"title\": \"Guest Posting - Crypto Web Wire\",\n      \"relevance_notes\": \"A dedicated news wire site focused on the web3 and crypto ecosystem. Promotes crypto developments through guest articles.\",\n      \"submission_url\": \"https://www.cryptowebwire.com/guest-posting\",\n      \"guidelines_snippet\": \"Promote your brand through guest posting on our dynamic platform. Reach a wider audience today! Contact: prdistributionpanel@gmail.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.cryptowallstreetnews.com/guest-posting\",\n      \"domain\": \"cryptowallstreetnews.com\",\n      \"type\": \"guest_post\",\n      \"title\": \"Guest Posting - Crypto Wallstreet News\",\n      \"relevance_notes\": \"Niche crypto news platform providing general blockchain news, startup features, and coin price predictions.\",\n      \"submission_url\": \"https://www.cryptowallstreetnews.com/guest-posting\",\n      \"guidelines_snippet\": \"Promote your brand through guest posting on our dynamic platform. Reach a wider audience today! Contact: prdistributionpanel@gmail.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.cryptowallstreetpress.com/guest-posting\",\n      \"domain\": \"cryptowallstreetpress.com\",\n      \"type\": \"guest_post\",\n      \